name: Custom Leather Saddle - Deerskin Tan
description:
Tan Custom Bicycle saddle covered in Deerskin Leather by hand. This is a one of a kind saddle. This custom saddle will stand out above the rest.

•CrMo Rails 
•Sporty shape and custom covers go well with any bike 
•302 grams

This is not just a cover or a old bicycle seat recovered, this is a new saddle custom covered for you.

For more saddles visit my Etsy Shop!  https://www.etsy.com/shop/JustOneCustomBicycle
